data.title: Tameka Foster - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Tameka Foster: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Celebrity hair stylist who gained fame as the former wife of singer Usher. She became a cast member on VH1's Atlanta Exes in 2014. She has worked with Patti LaBelle and Nas, among others.

Before Fame

She graduated from the Fashion Institute of Design and Merchandising in 1994.

Trivia

She founded The Lost Ones Foundation, a non-profit for teenage girls, in 2009. She has accumulated more than 120,000 followers on her TamekaRaymond X profile.

Family Life

She had a two-year marriage to Usher Raymond that ended in 2009, and she has five children: Darren, Ryan, Kile, Usher V, and Naviyd Eli.
